INSERT INTO `sline_line` VALUES
('8','0','8','许亭水库皮划艇+钓鱼+烧烤','','0','45','石家庄','2016-06-14','35','1','0','/uploads/2016/0331/00a10686cbeba1542fa9e807eb7399f8.jpg','','','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　 &nbsp;&nbsp; 1近来很多人问我们，本周有活动吗。车加车网俱乐部经过实地探路、踩点，终于可以斩钉截铁的说：有！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　本周日我们到许亭水库来场聚会party~吧~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　见见那些平时自驾群里(QQ群号：285381306)聊的挺high，却从未谋面的；见见刚刚聊的还挺起劲，一说“请客吃饭”就潜水的……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　大家一起烧烤，吃吃喝喝，聊聊人生，谈谈理想。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　你以为只是这样？NO！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">    <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们还准备了皮划艇、三国杀、扑克、麻将……喜欢钓鱼的朋友可以带上鱼杆，钓上一条大的你就赚了，嘿嘿~</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　带着老婆、孩子一起悠闲的度过这个周日吧，别忘了给孩子带上鱼网，孩子可以捞鱼。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　探路者回来很负责的说，这地方太适合孩子了~</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/themes/default/images/spacer.gif\" word_img=\"file:///E:\\Users\\Administrator.WIN-SO6AKLQE0QU\\AppData\\Roaming\\Tencent\\Users\\985102747\\QQ\\WinTemp\\RichOle\\IN0YMK3]5X7V@677TSG$RZ7.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221); background-image: url(http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/lang/zh-cn/images/localimage.png); background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/59171449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">活动说明：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.6000003814697px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong>本次活动以休闲、聚会为主，大家聊天、吃饭、钓鱼，玩皮划艇、打牌，想怎么玩怎么玩。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;许亭水库非旅游景点，地方不大，有一片湖水，一个草地＋树林，岸上有棵百年老树，岸边有些黄色小花。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;另，本次活动可带宠物，但要拿好牵引绳。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■</span>活动地点：</strong>许亭水库</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■</span>车程：</strong>约1小时</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■</span>集合地点：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　红旗南大街与南二环交叉口西南角</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■</span>集合时间：</strong>9月20日9：00</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名时间：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　即日起--2015年9月18日17：00</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■费用：</strong>35元/人（1.2米以下儿童免费）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名方式：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　1、在车加车网微信直接回复（公众号chejiache）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　2、发送短信：15530115819</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　3、电话报名：87885822 15530115819</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">    <strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■交费方式：</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　支付宝：3011930149@qq.com</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">　　华夏银行：6230 2000 8080 4680 刘文文</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  font-size: 14px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6000003814697px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">（其它支付方式可咨询电话87885822/15530115819）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/14821449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/34461449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/59701449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/43601449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/33651449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/70981449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/70301449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑;  text-align: center; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px;\">    <img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/99951449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/><img src=\"http://www.chejiache.com/res/js/dev/ueditor/php/upload/56361449042874.png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: none;\"/></p><p>    <br/></p>','','<p>本次活动以休闲、聚会为主，大家聊天、吃饭、钓鱼，玩皮划艇、打牌，想怎么玩怎么玩。</p><p>许亭水库非旅游景点，地方不大，有一片湖水，一个草地＋树林，岸上有棵百年老树，岸边有些黄色小花。</p><p>​另，本次活动可带宠物，但要拿好牵引绳。</p><p><br/></p>','','<p>​费用：35元/人（1.2米以下儿童免费），包括所有费用</p>','','','203',NULL,'45','自驾','3','1459240870','1465181153','','<p>​油费过路费以及个人消费自理</p>','','','1.2米以下儿童免费','45',NULL,'45,144','0','0','1','1','烧烤、钓鱼、皮划艇，还有比这更惬意的吗？','/uploads/2016/0331/ef797053ee5d10cee1e37f2814e179ce.jpg||,/uploads/2016/0331/00a10686cbeba1542fa9e807eb7399f8.jpg||,/uploads/2016/0331/991b69b0cd738359ba3a658d2369d763.jpg||',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1','1','line_new/line_show.htm','',NULL,'',NULL,'0','0','1','45');-- <xjx> --
