('9','0','9','草原天路自驾三日游','','0',NULL,'张北','2016-06-09','0','3','0','/uploads/2016/0621/4d2155c4fc4ca46afc8c0a9a0e5624a8.jpg','s:0:\"\";','','','<p><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/7a7031a3850a977a2f3a45bdcfddf1b1.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"3126\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: none rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(103, 103, 103) -1px 1px 2px; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 20px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(153, 153, 153) rgb(153, 153, 153); color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -38px 0px 0px 1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 18px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(255, 255, 255) rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\"></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: inherit;\"><section data-width=\"80%\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 534.391px; height: 40px; line-height: 1.5em; border-bottom-width: 5px; border-bottom-style: solid; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">活动说明：</span></strong></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　本次活动为自驾三日游，目的地为张北天路！将去大镜门、天鹅湖、安固里草原、风电主题公园、野狐岭要塞，品荞麦宴，赏篝火晚会！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　自驾活动过程中会穿插抽奖、抢红包等小游戏，奖品有小龙虾、牛排、免费清洗内饰、免费洗车＋打蜡等，绝对物超所值！！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　本次活动全程安全保障由斯托格专业汽车维修提供！<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■出发时间：6月9日--6月11日</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名时间：即日起--2016年6月7日12：00</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■车辆：限15辆车</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名费用：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　成人：488元/人</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　儿童：198元/人（1.2米以下，不占床）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■费用包含：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　门票：野狐岭军事要塞、草原天路、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">天鹅湖、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">安固里草原</span></span>；均为景区第一道门票，进入景区后产生的费用请自理。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　用餐：2早4正餐（两中两晚餐）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：AAA景区双人或三人标准间和县城准三酒店</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　领队：全程优秀自驾领队，导游服务</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　保险：旅行社责任险，旅游人身意外险。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■费用不含：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　1、过路费、油费及其他车辆费用；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2、景区或酒店内其他私人消费；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　3、其他个人行为产生的费用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名方式：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　1、在河北旅游网微信直接回复（公众号hebielvyouwang）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　2、加客服微信：18630172332</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　3、电话报名：87885822或<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">18630172332</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■报名格式：</span>姓名+联系方式+身份证号</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如：张笑笑+18630172332+130103198505060628，李非非、<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">130105198505060628</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">■交费方式：</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　支付宝帐号：18630172332 小游游</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　银行转帐：招商银行 6214 8331 1462 2742 &nbsp;刘文文</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">**报名后请在2016年6月7日17：00前，将费用交至账户中，最终参与人数以交费人数为准。因需要提前在张北订住宿及餐饮等事宜，报名后不参加活动仅退部分费用。</p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/9b264523107ecd8cbfcb6f09c0e80c62.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"3126\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: none rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(103, 103, 103) -1px 1px 2px; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 20px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(153, 153, 153) rgb(153, 153, 153); color: inherit;\"></section><section style=\"margin: -38px 0px 0px 1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 18px; border-style: solid; border-color: transparent transparent rgb(255, 255, 255) rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\"></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: inherit;\"><section data-width=\"80%\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 534.391px; height: 40px; line-height: 1.5em; border-bottom-width: 5px; border-bottom-style: solid; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><section style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">行程安排：</span></strong></section></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; padding: 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第一天（6月9号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　石家庄-张家口（约420公里，车程5.5小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早晨06:30石家庄指定地点集合，集体驾车赴张家口，到达<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【大境门景区】</span>（门票自理），游览、拍照，中餐处理。下午前往天然的草场<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【天鹅湖湿地】</span>，相比“大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆”的壮阔凄美，天鹅湖更多了一份蒙古族水泡子的神秘沧桑感。之后前往<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【风电主题公园】</span>，风电主题公园依托国家风光储输示范项目，国家风机检测中心和200万千瓦风电场而建，是集风电观光、新能源科普、星级酒店为一体的全国最大的风电主题公园。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：晚餐</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">－－</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">荞麦宴</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：张北双人标间</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第二天（6月10号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　张北-天路</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早餐后前往<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【草原天路】</span>，号称“中国66号公路”。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">沿线蜿蜒曲折、河流山峦、沟壑纵深、草甸牛羊、景观奇峻，展现出一幅百里坝头风景画卷。一同在特色酒店进行午餐，休息后到达安固里景区，接受蒙古族最崇高的礼仪迎接。晚餐可自费品尝烤全羊，用餐中观看<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">【大型草原歌舞演出】</span>，餐后广场互动<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">【篝火晚会】</span>开始，有安代舞，筷子舞，兔子舞，羌姆舞，大秧歌等等，在张北草原上度过难忘的夜晚。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：午餐，晚餐</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：景区蒙古包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第三天（6月11号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　张北-石家庄<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（约420公里，车程5.5小时）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早餐后前往张北县<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【野狐岭要塞】</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">矗立的碉堡、神秘的地道、燃烧的战火、弥漫的硝烟，一定会给您带来全新的军事体验</span>。中午返回县城，午餐后返回石家庄，结束本次天路之行。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 22.4px; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：午餐</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：无</p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p></section><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"85927\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 670px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(216, 40, 33);\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">温馨提示</span></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(216, 40, 33);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1. 草原紫外线很强，应戴太阳镜、帽子，并涂抹防晒霜.【端午节期间早晚温差大，请自备厚外套】</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2. 请带必备旅游用品、小药品、及防晒用品。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3. 草原节假日人流量较大，请听从领队安排前进。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4. 游览注意安全，品尝当地小吃要注意卫生和适量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、此行路途较远，请提前检查车况或进行保养，驾龄不满一年不建议参加活动。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6、路上我们会安排停靠服务区休息，请大家配合。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">7、本次活动费用含晚餐，如因自身原因放弃用餐，则餐费不退。</p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/11b7a0c224643d9d8e7193193a13e87e.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"32\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><blockquote style=\"margin: 3px; padding: 10px 15px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-top-left-radius: 50px; border-bottom-right-radius: 50px; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 5px 5px 2px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><section class=\"\" data-style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);font-size: 18px;font-weight:bold;\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); color: inherit;\">联系我们</strong></span></p></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; min-height: 1.5em; color: inherit;\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">联系电话：87885822或18630172332</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">客服微信：18630172332 小游游</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">QQ群：285381306</span></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></div></section></blockquote></section></section></section></section></p><p><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/d712c8f1dbf5401999f9d62fc599e899.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/7f3dd2f8272a044e470378d4f304ec65.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src