rtant;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　支付宝帐号：18630172332 小游游</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　银行转帐：招商银行 6214 8331 1462 2742 &nbsp;刘文文</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">**报名后请在2016年6月7日17：00前，将费用交至账户中，最终参与人数以交费人数为准。因需要提前在张北订住宿及餐饮等事宜，报名后不参加活动仅退部分费用。</p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/2e55d44a1223e847e919987eb0ec0ddc.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"3126\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: none rgb(107, 77, 64);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 40px; height: 40px; float: right; color: inherit; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 1px; box-shadow: rgb(103, 103, 103) -1px 1px 2px; co