m; white-space: normal; color: inherit; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); color: inherit; font-family: inherit;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第一天（6月9号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　石家庄-张家口（约420公里，车程5.5小时）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早晨06:30石家庄指定地点集合，集体驾车赴张家口，到达<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【大境门景区】</span>（门票自理），游览、拍照，中餐处理。下午前往天然的草场<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【天鹅湖湿地】</span>，相比“大漠孤烟直，长河落日圆”的壮阔凄美，天鹅湖更多了一份蒙古族水泡子的神秘沧桑感。之后前往<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【风电主题公园】</span>，风电主题公园依托国家风光储输示范项目，国家风机检测中心和200万千瓦风电场而建，是集风电观光、新能源科普、星级酒店为一体的全国最大的风电主题公园。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：晚餐</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">－－</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">荞麦宴</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：张北双人标间</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第二天（6月10号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　张北-天路</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早餐后前往<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【草原天路】</span>，号称“中国66号公路”。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">沿线蜿蜒曲折、河流山峦、沟壑纵深、草甸牛羊、景观奇峻，展现出一幅百里坝头风景画卷。一同在特色酒店进行午餐，休息后到达安固里景区，接受蒙古族最崇高的礼仪迎接。晚餐可自费品尝烤全羊，用餐中观看<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">【大型草原歌舞演出】</span>，餐后广场互动<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">【篝火晚会】</span>开始，有安代舞，筷子舞，兔子舞，羌姆舞，大秧歌等等，在张北草原上度过难忘的夜晚。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 22.4px; font-weight: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：午餐，晚餐</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：景区蒙古包</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　第三天（6月11号）</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　张北-石家庄<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">（约420公里，车程5.5小时）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　早餐后前往张北县<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">【野狐岭要塞】</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">矗立的碉堡、神秘的地道、燃烧的战火、弥漫的硝烟，一定会给您带来全新的军事体验</span>。中午返回县城，午餐后返回石家庄，结束本次天路之行。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 22.4px; text-decoration: inherit;\">　　用餐：午餐</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; line-height: 22.4px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　住宿：无</p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></p></section><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"85927\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; width: 670px; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(216, 40, 33);\"><span class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">温馨提示</span></section><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 1px solid rgb(216, 40, 33);\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1. 草原紫外线很强，应戴太阳镜、帽子，并涂抹防晒霜.【端午节期间早晚温差大，请自备厚外套】</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2. 请带必备旅游用品、小药品、及防晒用品。 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3. 草原节假日人流量较大，请听从领队安排前进。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4. 游览注意安全，品尝当地小吃要注意卫生和适量。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、此行路途较远，请提前检查车况或进行保养，驾龄不满一年不建议参加活动。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6、路上我们会安排停靠服务区休息，请大家配合。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">7、本次活动费用含晚餐，如因自身原因放弃用餐，则餐费不退。</p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/9417229316d8f340fc4abbeb1e11fd8b.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"32\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><blockquote style=\"margin: 3px; padding: 10px 15px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); border-top-left-radius: 50px; border-bottom-right-radius: 50px; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 5px 5px 2px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\"><section class=\"\" data-style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64);font-size: 18px;font-weight:bold;\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(107, 77, 64); line-height: 2em; font-size: 20px; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-color: rgb(107, 77, 64); color: inherit;\">联系我们</strong></span></p></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; min-height: 1.5em; color: inherit;\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">联系电话：87885822或18630172332</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">客服微信：18630172332 小游游</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\">QQ群：285381306</span></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px;\"><br/></span></div></section></blockquote></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">1、过路费、油费及其他车辆费用；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">2、景区或酒店内其他私人消费；</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 4px 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-size: 14px; line-height: 30px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\">3、其他个人行为产生的费用。</p><p><br/></p>','','','1.2米以下儿童免费198','49',NULL,'45,144','0','30','0','1','错峰出行赏天路美景','/uploads/2016/0621/4d2155c4fc4ca46afc8c0a9a0e5624a8.jpg||',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1','1','line_show.htm','',NULL,'',NULL,'0','0','1','49');-- <xjx> --
INSERT INTO `sline_line` VALUES
('10','0','10','紫云山自驾一日游','','0','45','石家庄','2016-06-08','0','1','0','/uploads/2016/0621/3d709e0208f0cacef8f616cde5429e58.jpg','s:0:\"\";','','','<section class=\"\" data-id=\"85636\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 5px 5px 0px; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><section class=\"\" data-style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　本次活动为自驾游，目的地是紫云山。单程约1.5小时，游玩一天，约16：00返程，到达石家庄的时间大约是17：30。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　因下高速后有部分的省道和县道，有拉货的大车经过，为了避免与大车抢道，保证安全，本次活动将错峰出行，集合时间为早7：00。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　山上有很多香椿树，带好装香椿的工具，采摘时请温柔。另有其它果树，还没成熟前，请手下留情。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　寻宝活动中的奖品将穿插在上山途中，一定要跟好我们的队伍，不然找不到奖品哦~奖品有紫云山门票（5张）、密室逃脱门票（30张）、麻辣小龙虾（3斤）……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">■ 活动时间：2016年5月8日 早7:00</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名时间：即日起--2016年5月7日12：00</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名费用：30元/成人(含午餐)儿童票电询</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 交费支付宝：3011930149@qq.com（其它支付方式可咨询电话87885822/15530115819）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 集合地点：西柏坡高速霍寨口</p></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"85636\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 5px 5px 0px; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 8px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left; font-style: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: transparent;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">报名须知</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; width: 0px; border-right-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-right-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 4px !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 4px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span>　　报名后工作人员将在24小时内通知大家，请保持手机畅通。交费后请务必按时到达集合地点，个人原因不能到场者费用不退哦。<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 车辆限制：本次自驾为用户体验活动，仅限15辆车，报满为止 （拒绝空降）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名方式：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、在河北旅游网微信直接回复（公众号hebeilvyouwang）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、发送短信：15530115819</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、电话报名：87885822/15530115819</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名格式：</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">报名+参与人数+是否有车+电话</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如：报名+3人+有车+13933112255</p></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; height: 0px; clear: both;\"></section></section><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" data-id=\"85636\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border: 0px none;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 5px 5px 0px; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 8px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left; font-style: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; background-color: transparent;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">温馨提示</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; width: 0px; border-right-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-right-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 4px !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 4px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><section class=\"\" data-style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1、经西柏坡高速，上高速时过路费自理，谢绝驾龄不满一年的新手司机。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2、午餐为五个凉菜、小米绿豆汤、大锅菜、馒头</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3、山路虽然好走，但拒绝高跟鞋、拖鞋等不适合上山的鞋</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4、有手台的朋友请带上，频率：400.1</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5、山上虽然时不时就有一棵香椿树，但请自备收集工具，温柔采摘</p></section></section></section><section class=\"\" label=\"powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/e7846343cd22834100f2e81adae50904.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/d459092ac23aeb9bb8d9f7c94d012935.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/><img src=\"/uploads/2016/0621/eedfa24f3fc986d1c3ac48f0b1c9b248.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"/>​</p></section></section></section></p>','','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: inherit; font-family: 微软雅黑; l