15530115819</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-weight: bold; line-height: 32px; text-align: justify; border-color: rgb(12, 137, 24); color: rgb(12, 137, 24); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\">■&nbsp;</span>报名格式：</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　报名+参与人数+是否有车+电话＋是否愿意搭载他人</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　如：报名+3人+有车+13933112255＋愿意</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　　　报名+2人+无车+13922112233</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">备注：</strong>车友如愿意搭载他人，我们会将电话告知没车参与者，请没车的参与者自行联系有车的，商讨搭车细节。</span></p><p><br/></p>','','<p>​20元/人 ，1.2米以下儿童10元/人（含保险/停车费/门票/水）</p>','','','269',NULL,'65','自驾','1','1459243773','1466502270','<section style=\"margin: 10px 8px 0px -8px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-style: inherit; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); float: left; text-decoration: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 0px 0.5em 0.5em 0px; display: inline-block; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(30, 155, 232);\"><strong class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">活动说明</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; width: 0px; border-right-width: 4px; border-right-style: solid; border-top-width: 4px; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-right-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); border-left-width: 4px !important; border-left-style: solid !important; border-left-color: transparent !important; border-bottom-width: 4px !important; border-bottom-style: solid !important; border-bottom-color: transparent !important;\"></section></section><p><br/></p><section class=\"\" data-style=\"box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 25.6000003814697px; background-color: rgb(244, 244, 244);\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: inherit; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 25.6px;\"></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　本次活动为自驾游，目的地是紫云山。单程约1.5小时，游玩一天，约16：00返程，到达石家庄的时间大约是17：30。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　因下高速后有部分的省道和县道，有拉货的大车经过，为了避免与大车抢道，保证安全，本次活动将错峰出行，集合时间为早7：00。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　山上有很多香椿树，带好装香椿的工具，采摘时请温柔。另有其它果树，还没成熟前，请手下留情。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　寻宝活动中的奖品将穿插在上山途中，一定要跟好我们的队伍，不然找不到奖品哦~奖品有紫云山门票（5张）、密室逃脱门票（30张）、麻辣小龙虾（3斤）……</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; line-height: 1.6;\">■ 活动时间：2016年5月8日 早7:00</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名时间：即日起--2016年5月7日12：00</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 报名费用：30元/成人(含午餐)儿童票电询</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 交费支付宝：3011930149@qq.com（其它支付方式可咨询电话87885822/15530115819）</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">■ 集合地点：西柏坡高速霍寨口</p></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>','<p>​油费过路费以及个人消费自理</p>','','','1.2米以下儿童15元','45',NULL,'45,144','0','15','0','1','爬山玩水，享受自然风光','/uploads/2016/0621/3d709e0208f0cacef8f616cde5429e58.jpg||,/uploads/2016/0621/b7433a8cbfb617cdd0c4a2f928185a7e.jpg||',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1','1','line_show.htm','',NULL,'',NULL,'0','0','1','45');-- <xjx> --
